==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quinquepartite
<hw>Quin*quep"ar*tite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>quinquepartitus</ets>; <ets>quinque</ets> five +
<ets>partitus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>partire</ets> to divide: cf. F.
<ets>quinqu⟦eacute⟧partite</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Consisting of five parts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Divided into five parts almost to
the base.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quinquereme</ent>⟦br⟧
